{"TopicId":135339,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"From VAB to game exit: 6 clicks and 2 loading screens","CreatedByName":"Yemo","CreatedById":114412,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:00:50Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Yemo","CreatedById":114412,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:00:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt currently requires 6 clicks and 2 loading screens to exit the game from the VAB. Could this be streamlined a bit without Alt\u002BF4?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:03:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs this is not new to the pre-1.1 release I\u0027ll move it to Suggestions \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Temeter","CreatedById":58056,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:04:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not just ALT\u002BF4 tho?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne thing that bothers me more is that I can\u0027t change controls without going to the main menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yemo","CreatedById":114412,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:10:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222482305\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459346642\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258056\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Temeter\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Temeter said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not just ALT\u002BF4 tho?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne thing that bothers me more is that I can\u0027t change controls without going to the main menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause it does not properly autosave the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:15:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222482324\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459347048\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114412\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Yemo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Yemo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause it does not properly autosave the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuick save first?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nF5 then Alt\u002BF4\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill faster than the usual\u00A0way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dfthu","CreatedById":80296,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:36:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut there should be a stock way instead of alt f4ing\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:38:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222482403\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459348618\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002280296\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dfthu\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Dfthu said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut there should be a stock way instead of alt f4ing\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n100% agreed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Exit to Windows\u0022 should be available in just about every scene except maybe when you are actually flying an active vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T14:39:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt might not be new to 1.1, but it should certainly be fixed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Temeter","CreatedById":58056,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T15:01:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222482403\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459348618\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002280296\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dfthu\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, Dfthu said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut there should be a stock way instead of alt f4ing\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222482410\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459348736\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n100% agreed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Exit to Windows\u0022 should be available in just about every scene except maybe when you are actually flying an active vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T19:14:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that in the difficulty settings of a save there is a setting that lets you quit to main menu from flight, VAB, SPH, and so on. Never tested it, but it might help having it start enabled.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T20:15:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222482410\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135339\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459348736\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Exit to Windows\u0022 should be available in just about every scene except maybe when you are actually flying an active vessel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy would I want to exit to \u0022Windows\u0022, I run a Linux machine here...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frank_G","CreatedById":100000,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-30T20:18:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn a Mac it is cmd-Q at any time, to quit the program from anywhere. I havent tried KSP\u00A0on my PC yet, (but will for sure, once my Oculus has arrived). Maybe a shortcut is available there too...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rath","CreatedById":138223,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-02T01:54:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCmd-q is my best friend when ksping in class\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}